{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/자동차박물관에서-이런-차가-좋았다","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c0bf99ba-e895-580a-a5ef-b7899ab7c11e","html":"<p>3월 초에 식구들과 자동차박물관을 찾았다. 원래는 아이들이 좋아할 것 같아서 갔는데 그렇지만은 않았다. 옛날식, 즉 구식인데도 한번씩 좋아지는 게 있다. 이런 거도 그 중 하나.\nSometimes I got fascinated by old-fashioned thingies. This is one of them.</p>\n<p>1955년식 <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercedes-Benz_300SL\" target=\"_blank\">메르세데스-벤츠 300SL Gullwing Coupé</a>. 3월초에 삼성 자동차박물관에서(Taken from the Samsung Cars Meseum early in March).</p>\n<div class=\"image-block\">\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/a3432/300SL.webp 350w,\n/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/426ac/300SL.webp 700w,\n/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/e46b2/300SL.webp 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/70ebb/300SL.jpg 350w,\n/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/29d31/300SL.jpg 700w,\n/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/6a068/300SL.jpg 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/0c0f276b45cf01f3cd30503b1361bb1f/6a068/300SL.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Mercedes Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955\"\n          title=\"Mercedes Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Mercedes Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</div>\n<!--more-->\n<div class=\"image-block\">\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/a3432/300SL2.webp 350w,\n/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/426ac/300SL2.webp 700w,\n/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/e46b2/300SL2.webp 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/70ebb/300SL2.jpg 350w,\n/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/29d31/300SL2.jpg 700w,\n/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/6a068/300SL2.jpg 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8e4d2c025d8c18077b428078e2021dfe/6a068/300SL2.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Mercedes-Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955\"\n          title=\"Mercedes-Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Mercedes-Benz 300SL Gullwing Coupé, 1955</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</div>\n<p>아래는 1985년 영화 <a href=\"http://movie.naver.com/movie/bi/mi/basic.nhn?code=10002\" target=\"_blank\">Back to the Future</a>의 명물 <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DeLorean_DMC-12\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"들로리안\">들로리안(DeLorian)</a>이다. 도장을 안하고 상용으로 출시된 독특한 차. 그러나 영화와 함께 그때 10대들은 열광했을 걸.\nThis is the famous Delorian from the movie Back to the Future, 1985. It was released at the market without painting its body. But I guess teenagers those days were all fascinated by the movie.</p>\n<div class=\"image-block\">\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/a3432/Delorian.webp 350w,\n/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/426ac/Delorian.webp 700w,\n/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/e46b2/Delorian.webp 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/70ebb/Delorian.jpg 350w,\n/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/29d31/Delorian.jpg 700w,\n/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/6a068/Delorian.jpg 960w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/5d78ab20d0f26a548e3c02cf9e464ed4/6a068/Delorian.jpg\"\n          alt=\"the Delorian\"\n          title=\"the Delorian\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">the Delorian</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n</div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/자동차박물관에서-이런-차가-좋았다","tagSlugs":["/tag/image/","/tag/들로리안/","/tag/백투더퓨처/","/tag/벤츠/","/tag/자동차박물관/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2013-03-18T16:26:48.000Z","description":"3월 초에 식구들과 자동차박물관을 찾았다. 원래는 아이들이 좋아할 것 같아서 갔는데 그렇지만은 않았다. 옛날식, 즉 구식인데도 한번씩 좋아지는 게 있다. 이런 거도 그 중 하나. Sometimes I got fascinated by old-fashioned thingies. This is one of them.","tags":["Image","들로리안","백투더퓨처","벤츠","자동차박물관"],"title":"자동차박물관에서 이런 차가 좋았다","socialImage":null,"featuredImage":null,"link":"http://start.goodtime.co.kr/2013/03/%ec%9e%90%eb%8f%99%ec%b0%a8%eb%b0%95%eb%ac%bc%ea%b4%80%ec%97%90%ec%84%9c-%ec%9d%b4%eb%9f%b0-%ec%b0%a8%ea%b0%80-%ec%a2%8b%ec%95%98%eb%8b%a4/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/자동차박물관에서-이런-차가-좋았다"}}}